{"tid":1502594,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"我有朋友form左條中醫team，可以幫中左tg毒嘅手足","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T03:16:07.000Z","uid":49898,"like":81,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"bef592ac95426f95cbaa9199faab1d3e10038182","tid":1502594,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:46:32.000Z","msg":"頭先係隔離post睇到有手足今日用機check到啲彈真係有山埃毒<br />\n<br />\n之前已經都有好多手足中左tg之後，又痾又嘔，聲沙眼朦，皮膚有問題，女仔仲要黎m都有問題<br />\n<br />\n我有fd form左中醫team<br />\nTG ID: cmed4brosis<br />\n<br />\n佢地話睇左幾十個症喳<br />\n有咩可能咁少出事，淨係我身邊都有幾個瀨左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽講有中左毒嘅手足去左睇西醫都搞唔掂，但佢地中醫都幫到下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望佢地幫到你地<br />\n我唔希望我地贏係要用你地條命去換返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd8d54f170cf2be8774c9123c6d1864ea4b2a8d","tid":1502594,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ac16682e5c55a82fe2609e4674e64c6bc062ff53","tid":1502594,"uid":195904,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:48:55.000Z","msg":"阿蛇唔洗行咇咩<br />\n咁得閒上網？"},{"pid":"a39698fd84a6da1a9df0ff6bd964f10c473894ee","tid":1502594,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac16682e5c55a82fe2609e4674e64c6bc062ff53","tid":1502594,"uid":195904,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:48:55.000Z","msg":"阿蛇唔洗行咇咩<br />\n咁得閒上網？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:51:04.000Z","msg":"我知宜家人心惶惶<br />\n你tg同佢地傾下咪知真定假"},{"pid":"471d886d517587403886146e854fd5b6d14538e6","tid":1502594,"uid":38109,"like":0,"disl